name: extreme_with_shadow_outer_restored_after_inner_expression
section: binding-scope-deep
args: outer:Int inner:Int offset:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Lexical binding and shadowing must preserve dependency order and branch-local scope.
law: (with [x {outer}] (= (+ (with [x {inner}] (+ x {offset})) x) (+ (+ {inner} {offset}) {outer})))
